==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Santalaceous
<hw>San`ta*la"ceous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to a natural order of plants
(<ord>Santalaceae</ord>), of which the genus <gen>Santalum</gen> is the
type, and which includes the buffalo nut and a few other North American
plants, and many peculiar plants of the southern hemisphere.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Santalic</ent>⟦br⟧
